title: Elegant Grand & Syndicate Top Floor Apartment
posting_body: ['Property Address', '35 Syndicate St S - 401 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 08/05/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Elegant Grand & Syndicate Top Floor Apartment', 'Bask in natural lighting in the B floor design.', "An in-home washer, dryer, and dishwasher add a convenient and contemporary touch to St. Paul's historic Grand Avenue.", 'Life is unforgettable in this upscale apartment.', 'Its built-in desk is the perfect organizational center.', "Enjoy the perks of being within walking distance to some of St. Paul's trendiest shops and cafes.", 'Residents at Grand & Syndicate apartments enjoy luxury finishes, rooftop community spaces, heated parking, private laundry, and hard surface flooring in the comfort of a newer smoke-free building.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Keyless Entry', 'Washer/Dryer in Apt', 'Granite Countertop', "9' Ceilings", 'Rooftop Lounge & Patio', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Elevator', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Vinyl Tile Plank Flooring', 'Fitness at the Grand Clubhouse', 'Online Rent Payment Portal', '24-hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Smoke-Free Living', 'Management Office on-site', 'Year Built: 2018', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 676', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,690.00', 'Available: 08/05/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
